results.name: Size of the key space for isomorphism verification of circulant graphs of order n.
comment: Multiplicative with a(p^m) = Catalan(m) (A000108). Coincides with A066060 up to n=63 except for n=32.
reference: M. Muzychuk, A solution of the isomorphism problem for circulant graphs, Proc. London Math. Soc. (3) 88 (2004), no. 1, 1-41.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
Index entries for sequences computed from exponents in factorization of n
formula: a(n) = prod_p Catalan(m_p) where n=prod_p p^(m_p), p|n prime.
maple: A069739 := proc(n) local ifa; if n = 1 then 1; else ifa := ifactors(n)[2] ; mul( A000108(op(2,f)), f=ifa) ; end if; end proc:
mathematica: Table[Times @@ Map[CatalanNumber, FactorInteger[n][[All, -1]]], {n, 90}] (* _Michael De Vlieger_, May 28 2017 *)
results.author: _Valery A. Liskovets_, Apr 15 2002
